				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Ladies and Gentlemen of the Everquest Community!<a name="63531"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Sep 22 04 8:33 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Ladies and Gentlemen of the Everquest Community,
<br />

<br />
	It has been far to long that we, the Everquest community, have been ignored by SoE. Let me point out some facts...
<br />

<br />
1) Why do almost all our questions get ignored?
<br />
2) Why is it that we play a GAME and get punished with nerfs/stupid expansions/terrible GM service/horrific game bugs?
<br />
3) Why is it that we ask them to fix the stuff that is broken in the game and we get ignored?
<br />

<br />
Do you, the Everquest community, know how much money SoE pulls in each month? Let me show you some rough figures...
<br />

<br />
1) There are 49 servers online
<br />
2) 1 account costs 12.95 per month
<br />
3) Let's say, there is roughly 1500 accounts per server (But we all know there is more)
<br />
4) Per month they make, $951,825.00
<br />
5) Per day they make, $31,727.50
<br />
6) Per hour they make, $1,321.97
<br />

<br />
Now that is a rough estimate...probably really close.
<br />

<br />
So now I ask you, why is it we put up with there crap?
<br />

<br />
If we as a community came together FULL force, we could make changes.
<br />

<br />
Now before you say, go away you whiner...we dont care. Listen to me for a second.
<br />

<br />
Have you ever said to yourself, God that is stupid why did they do that? Then you are in the same place as the rest of us.
<br />

<br />
I AM VOTING FOR A BAN OF EVERQUEST FOR 1 DAY...THATS RIGHT 1 DAY.
<br />

<br />
If you cancel your account and not play 1 day...you will cause them to lose $31,727.50
<br />

<br />
Thats alot of money, thats there pay checks. If you go 2 days, $63,455. Now we all know you can go 1 day without Everquest, but 2 days would be supreme. THEY WILL HEAR THE EVERQUEST COMMUNITY IF YOU MESS WITH THERE MONEY.
<br />

<br />
PLEASE, LETS COME TOGETHER AS A COMMUNITY AND SAY, WE WILL NOT STAND FOR YOUR IGNORANCE ANYMORE. EVERYONE CANCEL YOUR ACCOUNT AND WHEN ITS TIME TO RENEW, WAIT 1 OR 2 DAYS.
<br />

<br />
ALL I AM ASKING FOR IS 1 DAY...1 DAY WHERE YOU GO OUTSIDE AND PLAY WITH YOUR FAMILY...1 DAY WHERE YOU GO TO THE STORE AND SHOP...1 DAY WHERE YOU GO TO A MOVIE.
<br />

<br />
Please post this on any and every Everquest board you guys know of...AND WE WILL BE HEARD!</span></td>
